<body>
<segment id="1" parent="1001" relname="span">Have Clothes Custom</segment>
<segment id="2" parent="1" relname="elaboration">Made in Hong Kong</segment>
<segment id="3" parent="1004" relname="span">Custom clothes have been a traditional souvenir of visiting China</segment>
<segment id="4" parent="3" relname="circumstance">since Hong Kong belonged to China the first time .</segment>
<segment id="5" parent="1007" relname="condition">If you have clothes</segment>
<segment id="6" parent="1007" relname="span">custom made in Hong Kong ,</segment>
<segment id="7" parent="1009" relname="span">you ca n&apos;t expect the deeply discounted prices</segment>
<segment id="8" parent="7" relname="elaboration">you &apos;ll find on the mainland ,</segment>
<segment id="9" parent="1010" relname="span">but you can come home with an exquisite suit or dress</segment>
<segment id="10" parent="1011" relname="joint">made with fine fabrics</segment>
<segment id="11" parent="1012" relname="span">and cut exactly</segment>
<segment id="12" parent="11" relname="purpose">to fit your form .</segment>
<segment id="13" parent="1014" relname="preparation">Steps</segment>
<segment id="14" parent="1015" relname="span">Create some preliminary ideas or sketches</segment>
<segment id="15" parent="14" relname="circumstance">before you even leave your country of origin .</segment>
<segment id="16" parent="1018" relname="circumstance">When getting clothes</segment>
<segment id="17" parent="1018" relname="span">custom made in Hong Kong</segment>
<segment id="18" parent="17" relname="elaboration">you should be prepared .</segment>
<segment id="19" parent="1021" relname="span">You &apos;re very likely to spend much more</segment>
<segment id="20" parent="19" relname="antithesis">than you budgeted for ,</segment>
<segment id="21" parent="1022" relname="span">and be less happy with the final result</segment>
<segment id="22" parent="21" relname="condition">if you go without a plan or idea .</segment>
<segment id="23" parent="1025" relname="span">It can be a good idea</segment>
<segment id="24" parent="23" relname="purpose">to make your custom clothes part of your travel budget .</segment>
<segment id="25" parent="1025" relname="elaboration">You &apos;ll spend several hundred U.S. dollars on a quality Hong Kong tailor .</segment>
<segment id="26" parent="1027" relname="contrast">Talk to several tailors by phone</segment>
<segment id="27" parent="1028" relname="span">or contact them via email</segment>
<segment id="28" parent="27" relname="purpose">to get an idea of their availability and prices .</segment>
<segment id="29" parent="1014" relname="joint">The best tailors wo n&apos;t be available on a drop-in basis ,</segment>
<segment id="30" parent="1031" relname="preparation">so you can make an appointment</segment>
<segment id="31" parent="1031" relname="joint">as your travel plans are arranged .</segment>
<segment id="32" parent="1031" relname="joint">You can find information about tailors in Hong Kong from recently-updated guidebooks for the city .</segment>
<segment id="33" parent="1034" relname="span">Another technique is to contact the hotel</segment>
<segment id="34" parent="33" relname="elaboration">where you &apos;ll be staying .</segment>
<segment id="35" parent="1036" relname="preparation">With tailored clothing being such a draw in Hong Kong tourism ,</segment>
<segment id="36" parent="1036" relname="joint">the concierge is almost guaranteed to have a relationship with at least one tailor .</segment>
<segment id="37" parent="1038" relname="span">Visit the tailors</segment>
<segment id="38" parent="37" relname="elaboration">you &apos;re considering early during your stay in Hong Kong .</segment>
<segment id="39" parent="1036" relname="joint">View fabric samples ,</segment>
<segment id="40" parent="1041" relname="sequence">talk about pricing</segment>
<segment id="41" parent="1042" relname="span">and look at finished garments</segment>
<segment id="42" parent="41" relname="circumstance">before committing to one tailor .</segment>
<segment id="43" parent="1036" relname="joint">It &apos;s best to set aside at least half a day for this research .</segment>
<segment id="44" parent="1036" relname="joint">Set aside another half day for your fitting and initial negotiation with your tailor .</segment>
<segment id="45" parent="1047" relname="span">Bring sketches or photos from fashion magazines</segment>
<segment id="46" parent="45" relname="purpose">to help communicate exactly the kind of garment</segment>
<segment id="47" parent="1047" relname="elaboration">you want .</segment>
<segment id="48" parent="49" relname="condition">If you have a favorite suit , dress or other set of clothing ,</segment>
<segment id="49" parent="1050" relname="span">you can bring it to the tailor ,</segment>
<segment id="50" parent="1036" relname="joint">and he will produce additional copies in different fabrics and colors .</segment>
<segment id="51" parent="1052" relname="span">Expect to pay a 50 percent deposit</segment>
<segment id="52" parent="51" relname="circumstance">before your tailor will begin work .</segment>
<segment id="53" parent="1054" relname="same_unit">Prior to paying that deposit ,</segment>
<segment id="54" parent="1054" relname="same_unit">get a written agreement on price and due date .</segment>
<segment id="55" parent="1056" relname="span">Quality tailoring takes from several days to 1 week ,</segment>
<segment id="56" parent="55" relname="purpose">so it &apos;s best to get to this stage early during your vacation in Hong Kong .</segment>
<segment id="57" parent="1036" relname="joint">Pick up your garment on the due date .</segment>
<segment id="58" parent="1059" relname="span">Check quality</segment>
<segment id="59" parent="58" relname="circumstance">before you pay ,</segment>
<segment id="60" parent="1036" relname="joint">and negotiate for any needed alterations .</segment>
<segment id="61" parent="1061" relname="preparation">Tips</segment>
<segment id="62" parent="1062" relname="span">Avoid tailors</segment>
<segment id="63" parent="62" relname="elaboration">who offer package deals .</segment>
<segment id="64" parent="1064" relname="span">The best tailors will make your clothing exactly to order ,</segment>
<segment id="65" parent="64" relname="manner">without adding extra garments .</segment>
<segment id="66" parent="1066" relname="span">Establishments with those package deals work to templates ,</segment>
<segment id="67" parent="1067" relname="span">trusting the fact</segment>
<segment id="68" parent="67" relname="elaboration">that the tourist market does n&apos;t represent many return customers .</segment>
<segment id="69" parent="1066" relname="motivation">Burlington Arcade on Nathan Road is famous for its wide selection of quality and reasonably-priced tailors .</segment>
